---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import Subheading from "../components/Subheading.astro";
---

<PageLayout title="Code of Conduct">
  <div class="article-wrapper">
    <article id="code-of-conduct" class="classic-bg">
      <Subheading title="Code of Conduct" />
      <foreground>
        <text-container>

          <p> All users, contributors, and moderators of Technolgap are expected to abide by our Code of
            Conduct, both online and during in-person events hosted and/or associated with Technolgap. </p>
          
          <h3> The Pledge </h3>
          <p> In the interest of fostering an open and welcoming environment, we pledge to make participation
          in our community a harassment-free experience for everyone, regardless of age, body size,
          disability, ethnicity, gender identity and expression, level of experience, nationality, personal
          appearance, race, religion, or sexual identity and orientation. </p>

          <h3> Core Values </h3>
          <values> Respect </values>
          <values> Inclusivity </values>
          <values> Integrity </values>
          <values> Transparency </values>

          <h3> Expected Behavior </h3>
          <bullet> Using welcoming and inclusive language. </bullet>
          <bullet> Being respectful of differing viewpoints and experiences. </bullet>
          <bullet> Gracefully accepting constructive criticism. </bullet>
          <bullet> Referring to people by their preferred pronouns and using gender-neutral pronouns when uncertain. </bullet>

          <h3> Unacceptable Behavior </h3>
          <bullet> Harassment, trolling, or derogatory comments. </bullet>
          <bullet> Sharing others' private information without permission. </bullet>
          <bullet> Ignoring reasonable communication boundaries. </bullet>
          <bullet> Using sexualized language or imagery. </bullet>
          <bullet> Swearing or using disturbing language. </bullet>
          <bullet> Engaging in political arguments. </bullet>
          <bullet> Promoting inequality or drug use. </bullet>
          <bullet> Attacking personal tastes. </bullet>
          <bullet> Any conduct inappropriate in a professional setting. </bullet>

          <h3>Reporting Violations</h3>
          <p> If you encounter or witness any violations of this code of conduct, please report them
            immediately to info@technolgap.org. All reports will be handled with confidentiality and
            sensitivity. We reserve the right and responsibility to remove comments or other contributions
            that are not aligned with this code of conduct, or to ban temporarily or permanently any
            members for other behaviors that are deemed inappropriate, threatening, offensive, or harmful. </p>

          <h3>Acknowledgement and Agreement</h3>
          <p> By using our website, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to abide by
            this code of conduct. We reserve the right to update this code as necessary and will notify users
            of any changes. </p>

          <h3>Contact Information</h3>
          <spread> Email Address: <a href="mailto:info@technolgap.org">info@technolgap.org</a> </spread>
          <spread> Emergency Services: 911 </spread>

        </text-container>
      </foreground>
  </div>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  article {
    padding-bottom: 5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 0;
    text-align: center;

    min-height: 100vh;
    background-size: cover;
    background-color: white;
    background-color: transparent;
    box-shadow: none;
    background-position: top center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: 100% auto;
  }
  .article-wrapper {
    background-color: white;
  }

  #code-of-conduct foreground {
    display: grid;
    background-color: #64a8a2;
    border-radius: 20px;
    row-gap: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 7px 10px 1px #898989;
    border: solid 5px #fee8f5;
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-bottom: 50px;
  }
  #code-of-conduct h3 {
    font-size: 30px;
    text-shadow: 
    1px 1px 0px #FFBCE5,
    -1px -1px 0px #FFBCE5,
    1px -1px 0px #FFBCE5,
    -1px 1px 0px #FFBCE5;
    color: white;
  }
  #code-of-conduct p {
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 18px;
    text-align: left;
    margin-left: 5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    margin-right: 5rem;
  }
  #code-of-conduct values {
    display: list-item;
    list-style-type: none;
    color: #FFBCE5;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-left: 2rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    margin-right: 2rem;
  }
  #code-of-conduct spread {
    display: block;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-left: 2rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    margin-right: 2rem;
  }
  #code-of-conduct bullet {
    display: list-item;
    list-style-type: disc;
    margin-left: 6rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 18px;
    text-align: left;
    margin-right: 5rem;
  }
  #code-of-conduct a {
    color: #ffffff;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  #code-of-conduct a:hover {
    color: #fee8f5;
    text-decoration: underline 2px solid #fee8f5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    #code-of-conduct h3 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    #code-of-conduct p,
    #code-of-conduct bullet,
    #code-of-conduct spread {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 1rem;
      margin-left: 2rem;
      margin-right: 2rem;
    }
    #code-of-conduct values {
      font-size: 16px;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 550px) {
    #code-of-conduct foreground {
      margin: 0 20px;
    }
    #code-of-conduct p,
    #code-of-conduct bullet,
    #code-of-conduct spread {
      margin: 1rem;
    }
    #code-of-conduct bullet {
      margin-left: 2rem;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 450px) {
    #code-of-conduct h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    #code-of-conduct p,
    #code-of-conduct bullet,
    #code-of-conduct spread {
      font-size: 12px;
      margin: 1rem;
    }
    #code-of-conduct bullet {
      margin: 2rem;
      margin-top: 0.125rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 350px) {
    #code-of-conduct h3 {
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    #code-of-conduct p,
    #code-of-conduct bullet,
    #code-of-conduct spread {
      font-size: 10px;

    }
    #code-of-conduct values {
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  }
</style>